1
00:00:57,080 --> 00:00:58,320
Something's wrong, Mr. Zheng

2
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,640
The Fifth Concubine is missing

3
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,840
When did it happen

4
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,840
She didn't return all last night

5
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,840
I searched everywhere

6
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:08,600
Then I found this in an alley near the house

7
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,760
This... th-that Madam

8
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,360
Something must've happened to the Fifth Concubine

9
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,600
What are we going to do

10
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:16,560
If Master finds out

11
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,720
he'll surely kill me

12
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,560
Where was it found

13
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:26,080
These hairs are stuck together

14
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,040
They're stuck together

15
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,320
It's real fox fur

16
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,200
It's real fox fur

17
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:44,560
Footprints this big don't look like a fox's

18
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:47,280
Then it must be an especially big fox

19
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,640
This really is an Apparition of the Fox Spirit

20
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,120
You may as well stop being a detective

21
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,240
and just go practice shamanism

22
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:57,480
Someone glued fox fur onto clothing

23
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,680
to fake the Fox Spirit causing trouble

24
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,040
Y-yes, yes, yes

25
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,040
That's right

26
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:04,440
This...

27
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:14,120
I feel I've seen petals like these before

28
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:29,840
Once I get rid of you meddling fool

29
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:33,000
only the last move will remain in this game

30
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,640
and it'll soon be done

31
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,680
Someone! Someone!

32
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,280
Quick, quick, light the candles

33
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:19,040
All right, you may go

34
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:39,040
Are you sure Madam is at the Lu family

35
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:40,800
The Lu family matriarch, Lu Xin

36
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,480
and Lu Quan, who was nearly murdered

37
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:43,760
they're all members of the Lu family

38
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,680
If the killer could poison them

39
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,120
then he's most likely at the Lu family now

40
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,280
I see

41
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,640
Don't fool me again about silver dollars on the ground

42
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,440
Come out and I'll give them to you

43
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:58,000
Fine. Remember this. Get up

44
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:04,680
It's poison from the Soul-Bewitching Herb

45
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:09,000
You must take the antidote at once

46
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,280
So it really was him

47
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:44,560
How did you know it was here

48
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,440
This is the room where Liu Xing was staying

49
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,600
The Apparition of the Fox Spirit was his trick

50
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,960
On the day of the Lu matriarch's funeral

51
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:54,080
I saw Liu Xing handling this potted flower

52
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,600
with extreme care

53
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,440
Zheng Yu, look at this

54
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,240
So that's how the Fox Spirit apparition was done

55
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,240
How is Madam

56
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:15,080
She's all right, she only fainted

57
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,520
Take care of Madam. I'll go after him

58
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,000
Y-you came

59
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,880
Save me, save me

60
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,720
Why

61
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:02,160
The Fox Spirit will be grateful to you

62
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,600
Liu Xing

63
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,720
Liu Xing

64
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,320
Liu Xing

65
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,920
You're awake

66
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,080
How are you feeling

67
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,000
Much better

68
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,840
Fifth Concubine

69
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,360
Fifth Concubine, you've finally returned

70
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,840
You had me worried sick

71
00:08:21,320 --> 00:08:22,760
Thank you for looking after me, Mr. Zheng

72
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,560
But instead of taking me back to the Wang Family

73
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:25,800
you brought me here to your place

74
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,240
That seems rather improper

75
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,080
If word gets out

76
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,360
the misunderstanding would be serious

77
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,520
So then

78
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,840
I was meddling where I shouldn't

79
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:39,440
I am, after all, the Wang Family's Fifth Concubine

80
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,280
Mr. Zheng, conduct yourself with dignity

81
00:08:42,280 --> 00:08:43,160
I'll be going back first

82
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,120
I'll send someone to deliver some silver dollars to you

83
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,960
so your efforts won't be for nothing, Mr. Zheng

84
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,040
How much longer will you remain the Fifth Concubine

85
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,240
M-Madam, why did she leave

86
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,400
Was Liu Xing found

87
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,840
Liu Xing is dead

88
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,400
Dead

89
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,400
And he died exactly like the first two victims

90
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,680
It seems there's another killer behind this

91
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,680
Who knows how deep this killer's grudge is against the Lu family

92
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:22,120
He's killed the Lu family down to Lu Quan alone
